** The Tradelink Opportunity **

  

Ready to take the next step in your career, help shape our success, all while
working with a genuinely fun team? How would you like to become our Digital
Product Owner?

  

** Why this Role **

**   
**

We know that you're passionate about helping people and businesses succeed. In
this role, you’ll get to do both. You will:

  

  * Have a passion for helping a business grow through your direct efforts 
  * Have the ability to drive adoption through deep engagement and understanding of our customers’ needs, branch and key sales staff, systems, and business processes 
  * Work closely with internal and external stakeholders to ensure the correct items and information displays, help implement promotions and brand messaging 
  * Participate in customer visits, feature launch events, in-store activities, training webinars, and retrospectives to constantly track our ROI and future focus 
  * Have the skills to be able to troubleshoot issues that both customers and staff 
You’ll love this role for the opportunity to see the results of your efforts
in action! There is also never a shortage of opportunities to build your
skills, and this role will give you great exposure. Another drawcard is our
team – you couldn’t find a more authentic and supportive bunch. Finally, we
have a long-term vision that we believe in, and love to try new things so your
ideas will always be heard.

  

At the same time, it’s true that not every job is for everyone. You will find
that this role will need you to pivot quickly and adapt to changing needs.
You'll be working in a super-fast environment with competing demands on your
time. Everyday you’ll need to bring high levels of energy and positivity for
your team members and stakeholders. Finally, you'll need to be comfortable
working hands-on, be self-directed, and resourceful.

  

** Why You **

  

So, what are we looking for? We are open to applicants from all walks of life
– we want you to use your diverse experiences to enrich the learnings you
share.

This role will be pivotal to the success of the digital business, we are
looking for someone to jump in and run with the product.

  

Most importantly, we’re looking for:

**   
**

  * Someone experienced with Jira, Confluence and key analytical tools such as Lucky Orange, UXCAM, Google Analytics (GA4) 
  * Familiar with Scaled Agile methodology 
  * Willingness to to work across 3 time zones – New Zealand, Australia and India 
  * Previous experience as a Product Owner. 
  * As a cherry-on-top, we’d be thrilled if you had a great sense of humour! 

** Why Tradelink **

  

Simple. We are about being Real People, Always

  

We’re a well-respected Australian plumbing distribution brand built on real,
hard-working people who never forget what the word ‘team’ means and who
understands true partnership; they help and back each other, our customers,
and our Fletcher Building Group colleagues. With branches across the country
and a support office that’s invested and evolving, the opportunities at
Tradelink are endless. We also love the challenge - Tradelink people have the
guts and heart to be bold, and we hope you will too. Because here your
successes will be seen, and you’ll feel every win!

  

On top of that, we offer some great benefits like our Employee Education Fund,
Share Purchase Scheme, Paid Parental Leave, Flexible Working, Discounts and
more. You will also have access to a fully funded tools-of-trade vehicle as
part of this role.

  

Are you ready to put your hand up and make this happen the Tradelink way?
Apply Now!

  

If you’re creative, agile and passionate about growth, then we can’t wait to
meet you and have you join our journey.

